{"tid":1957277,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"求解答，譴責受害人是不是必然錯誤的行為？","createTime":"2020-04-03T18:41:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T17:25:51.000Z","uid":348168,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5ace77dd73ffe3fb0571fe8af318b85b32a95ad4","tid":1957277,"uid":348168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T18:41:20.000Z","msg":"在一個<span style=\"color: red;\">危險而難以改變的環境/情況</span>下，某人雖知道該<span style=\"color: red;\">環境/情況</span>的<span style=\"color: gold;\">危險性</span>，卻不以為然，<span style=\"color: violet;\">採取了較危險的行動</span>，最終成為<span style=\"color: green;\">受害人</span>。那麼譴責這個<span style=\"color: green;\">人</span>是否有錯？<br />\n<br />\n例子A：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">十號風球懸掛</span>，知道這消息的<span style=\"color: green;\">蔡哥</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">選擇落街買零食，而非留在家中</span>，不幸<span style=\"color: gold;\">被吹倒的大樹壓死</span>，那麼<span style=\"color: green;\">蔡哥</span>是否應被譴責？<br />\n<br />\n例子B：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">某大廈的升降機經常出現故障</span>，知道這情況的<span style=\"color: green;\">馮哥</span>仍然<span style=\"color: violet;\">選擇乘升降機，而非行樓梯</span>，不幸<span style=\"color: gold;\">困𨋢</span>，那麼<span style=\"color: green;\">馮哥</span>是否應被譴責？<br />\n<br />\n例子C：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">某國的盜竊案特別多</span>，前往該國旅行的<span style=\"color: green;\">誠哥</span>知道這情況，卻在巴士上<span style=\"color: violet;\">選擇把手機放在褲袋，而非背囊</span>，不幸<span style=\"color: gold;\">被扒手盜走</span>，那麼<span style=\"color: green;\">誠哥</span>是否應被譴責？<br />\n<br />\n例子D：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">某區在一星期內發生了三宗強姦案，犯罪者仍未被捕</span>，知道這消息的<span style=\"color: green;\">阿遙</span>仍然<span style=\"color: violet;\">在晚上選擇穿著暴露性感，而非較為保守的衣服外出，或甚至不外出</span>，不幸<span style=\"color: gold;\">被強姦</span>，那麼<span style=\"color: green;\">阿遙</span>是否應被譴責？"},{"pid":"0e70c09189e3fdc571becb321c3cd9ad3cb84725","tid":1957277,"uid":312422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T19:04:16.000Z","msg":"A,B: 都冇影響他人，譴責啲咩？<br />\n<br />\nC,D: 引人犯罪的確有影響他人，但CD情況中，影響不足以有力推動到對方犯罪，所以不應譴責<br />\n<br />\n但有d情況e.g.撩交打，有力推動到對方犯罪，你勉強可以譴責嘅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申9up 請指正"},{"pid":"3c11664cf82431eca876ced1ede803da94999a09","tid":1957277,"uid":162456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T19:18:12.000Z","msg":"呃左30萬保釋金崔銳蛋想搵埋藍絲錢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NpziJe1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNpziJe1.jpg&h=5687ab64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6dae182b0f4c4f0058e0b826766d013c81f1313","tid":1957277,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e70c09189e3fdc571becb321c3cd9ad3cb84725","tid":1957277,"uid":312422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T19:04:16.000Z","msg":"A,B: 都冇影響他人，譴責啲咩？<br />\n<br />\nC,D: 引人犯罪的確有影響他人，但CD情況中，影響不足以有力推動到對方犯罪，所以不應譴責<br />\n<br />\n但有d情況e.g.撩交打，有力推動到對方犯罪，你勉強可以譴責嘅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申9up 請指正"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T19:30:47.000Z","msg":"例子A好似連加害者都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似連受害者都稱唔上？"},{"pid":"b05a2289161770248aaad7d58155cd84020e3b29","tid":1957277,"uid":200915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T19:33:01.000Z","msg":"其實呢強姦案好多時候個受害者都唔係著得曝露<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JG-ZSxhe_XM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJG-ZSxhe_XM&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQypmLjsYRFZgpJr%2B2v3iO%2BBA%3D&h=f8b71f70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JG-ZSxhe_XM</a><br />\n<br />\n同埋好多時候強姦係友姦比較多"},{"pid":"9f1b4acbbf92d0c443ad4a500b30cdd9c069945f","tid":1957277,"uid":348168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0e70c09189e3fdc571becb321c3cd9ad3cb84725","tid":1957277,"uid":312422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T19:04:16.000Z","msg":"A,B: 都冇影響他人，譴責啲咩？<br />\n<br />\nC,D: 引人犯罪的確有影響他人，但CD情況中，影響不足以有力推動到對方犯罪，所以不應譴責<br />\n<br />\n但有d情況e.g.撩交打，有力推動到對方犯罪，你勉強可以譴責嘅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申9up 請指正"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T19:35:47.000Z","msg":"譴責的意思並非斥責受害人對他人或對世界的影響。<br />\n譴責受害人你可以當成是認為受害人抵死。<br />\n比如譴責A的受害人：明知十號風球還要出街，蔡哥是抵死的。<br />\n譴責D的受害人：明知有強姦犯還要穿成這樣，阿遙是抵死的。<br />\n<br />\n例子當中，AB不存在加害人，CD存在加害人，有很多理論認為譴責受害人是錯誤的行為，因為會把責任從加害者移至受害者身上。<br />\n而例子ABCD中，都同樣是受害人採取了較危險的行動，所以才成為受害人。<br />\n那其實是不是無論事件中有否存在加害人，都應該譴責受害人？"},{"pid":"ce9710c9a1c18e10074b97b82f15686092a7a571","tid":1957277,"uid":348168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6dae182b0f4c4f0058e0b826766d013c81f1313","tid":1957277,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e70c09189e3fdc571becb321c3cd9ad3cb84725","tid":1957277,"uid":312422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T19:04:16.000Z","msg":"A,B: 都冇影響他人，譴責啲咩？<br />\n<br />\nC,D: 引人犯罪的確有影響他人，但CD情況中，影響不足以有力推動到對方犯罪，所以不應譴責<br />\n<br />\n但有d情況e.g.撩交打，有力推動到對方犯罪，你勉強可以譴責嘅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申9up 請指正"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T19:30:47.000Z","msg":"例子A好似連加害者都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似連受害者都稱唔上？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T19:47:17.000Z","msg":"咁如果將題目改成譴責不幸者如何？<br />\n例子ABCD中，都同樣是不幸者採取了較危險的行動，所以才遭遇不幸。<br />\n那其實是不是無論事件中有否存在加害人，都應該譴責不幸者？"},{"pid":"a58459bdd6ced9526aa2d5d50bce0eb964c68f0f","tid":1957277,"uid":348168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b05a2289161770248aaad7d58155cd84020e3b29","tid":1957277,"uid":200915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T19:33:01.000Z","msg":"其實呢強姦案好多時候個受害者都唔係著得曝露<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JG-ZSxhe_XM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJG-ZSxhe_XM&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQypmLjsYRFZgpJr%2B2v3iO%2BBA%3D&h=f8b71f70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JG-ZSxhe_XM</a><br />\n<br />\n同埋好多時候強姦係友姦比較多"},"citedBy":1,"rep